               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     3ra-112rb)
 I-1) Homily by Timothy (Dumatewos), Patriarch of Alexandria for
                     the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 3ra-9ra); commemorative notice (fols. 9ra-10vb); two
                     ʿarke-hymns (fols. 10vb-11ra); miracle (fols. 11ra-13ra)
 I-2) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for the 12th of Tāḫśāś (fols. 13ra-18va); commemorative notice
                     (fols. 18va-19ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 19ra-rb); miracle (fols. 19rb-20vb)
                     I-3) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the 12th of Ṭǝrr (fols.
                     20vb-29vb); commemorative notice (fols. 29vb-30ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 30ra);
                     miracle (fols. 30ra-31rb)
 I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th
                     of Yakkātit (fols. 31rb-34va); commemorative notice (fols. 34va-35ra);
                     ʿarke-hymn (fol. 35ra); miracle (fols. 35ra-36va)
 I-5) Homily by [Severus]
                     Patriarch of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 36va-51rb);
                     commemorative notice (fol. 51rb-va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 51va); miracle (fols.
                     51va-53va)
 I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] the Orthodox for the
                     12th of Miyāzyā (fols. 53va-57vb); commemorative notice (fols. 57vb-58rb);
                     miracle (fols. 58rb-61rb)
 I-7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, [Metropolitan] of
                     Ethiopia for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 61rb-63ra); commemorative notice (fol.
                     63ra-va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 63va); miracle (fols. 63va-66rb)
 I-8) Homily by
                     [Yoḥannǝs,] Metropolitan of ʾAksum (ʾAkʷǝsǝm) [for Sane] (fols. 66rb-72va);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 72va-79rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 79rb-va); miracle
                     (fols. 79va-82ra)
 I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for the 12th of
                     Ḥamle (fols. 82ra-86va); miracle (fols. 86va-88rb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     88rb-89ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 89ra)
 I-10) Homily by an anonymous author for
                     the 12th of Naḥāse (fols. 89ra-91vb); miracle (fols. 91vb-97rb); commemorative
                     notice (fol. 97rb-va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 97va-vb)
 I-11) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for the 12th of Maskaram (fols. 97vb-101va); commemorative
                     notice (fol. 101va-vb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 101vb); miracle (fols.
                     101vb-104vb)
 I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Ṭǝqǝmt
                     (fols. 104vb-109va); commemorative notice (fols. 109va-110rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol.
                     110rb-va); miracle (fols. 110va-112rb)</summary>
